<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>GitHub Copilot</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>GitHub Copilot</h1>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a></li>
        <li><a href="#get-started">Get Started</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section id="hero">
      <h2>Your AI Pair Programmer</h2>
      <p>GitHub Copilot helps you write code faster and smarter with AI-powered code suggestions directly in your editor.</p>
      <a href="#get-started" class="cta-button">Try Copilot</a>
    </section>
    <section id="features">
      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Real-time code suggestions as you type</li>
        <li>Supports multiple programming languages</li>
        <li>Context-aware completions</li>
        <li>Integrates with VS Code, Neovim, and more</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="how-it-works">
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p>GitHub Copilot uses powerful AI models trained on public code to predict and suggest code snippets, functions, and even entire classes based on your comments and code.</p>
    </section>
    <section id="get-started">
      <h2>Get Started</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Install the Copilot extension in your preferred editor</li>
        <li>Sign in with your GitHub account</li>
        <li>Start coding and let Copilot help!</li>
      </ol>
      <a href="https://github.com/features/copilot" target="_blank" class="cta-button">Learn More</a>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 GitHub Copilot. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
